quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,(hm) sabaq alkalam ealaa alhrwf almqttaet fi 'awal surat albqrt
  44,2,"aqsm allah taealaa bialquran alwadih lfzana wmena. 'iinaa 'anzalnah fi laylat alqadr almubarakat kathirat alkhyrat, wahi fi rmdan. 'iinaa kunaa mundhirin alnaas bima yanfaeuhum wydrhm, wdhlk bi'iirsal alrusul w'inzal alktb; ltqwm hujat allah ealaa ebadh. fiha yuqda wyufsl min allwh almhfwz 'iilaa alktbt min almalayikat kll 'amr mhkm min alajal walarzaq fi tilk alsnt, waghayr dhlk mimaa yakun fiha 'iilaa akhrha, la ybddal wala yghyar. hdha al'amr alhakim 'amr min endna, fjmye ma yakun wyqdrh allah taealaa wama ywhyh fbamrh w'idhnh welmh. 'iinaa kunaa mursilin 'iilaa alnaas alrusul mhmdana wamin qblh; rahmatan min rabik -ayha alrswl- balmrsl 'ilyhm. 'iinah hu alsamie yasmae jmye alaswat, alealim bjmye 'umur khalaqah alzzahirat walbatn. khaliq alsmwat wal'ard wama baynahuma min al'ashya' klha, 'iin kuntum muwqinin bdhlk faelamuu 'ana rabi almkhlwqat hu 'ilhha alhq. la 'ilh yastahiqu alebadt 'iilaa hu wahdah la sharik lh, yuhyi wymyt, rabukum warabu abayikum alawlyn, faebuduh dun alihatakum alty la tuqadar ealaa durin wala nfe"
  44,3,"'uqsim allah taealaa bialquran alwadih lfzana wamaenaa. 'iinaa 'anzalnah fi laylat alqadr almubarakat kathirat alkhayrati, wahi fi ramdanin. 'iinaa kunaa mundhirin alnaas bima yanfaeuhum wayaduruhum, wdhlk bi'iirsal alrusul wa'iinzal alkatba; litaqum hujat allah ealaa eibadih. fiha yuqda wyufsl min allawh almahfuz 'iilaa alktbt min almalayikat kll 'amr mahkum min alajal wal'arzaq fi tilk alsanati, waghayr dhlk mimaa yakun fiha 'iilaa akhiriha, la ybddal wala yghyar. hdha al'amr alhakim 'amr min eindina, fajmie ma yakun wayuqdiruh allah taealaa wama yuhiuh fabi'amarih wa'iidhanih waeilmiha. 'iinaa kunaa mursilin 'iilaa alnaas alrusul mhmdana wamin qabliha; rahmat min rabik -'ayaha alrasula- bialmursil 'iilayhim. 'iinah hu alsamie yasmae jmye al'aswati, alealim bijamie 'umur khalaqah alzzahirat walbatinata. khaliq alsamawat wal'ard wama baynahuma min al'ashya' kulaha, 'iin kuntum muwqinin bdhlk faelamuu 'ana rabi almakhluqat hu 'iilahuha alhuqa. la 'iilah yastahiqu aleibadat 'iilaa hu wahdah la sharik laha, yuhyi waymaytu, rabukum warabu abayikum al'awalina, faebuduh dun alihatakum alty la tuqadar ealaa durin wala nafae"
  44,4,"'uqsim allah taealaa bialquran alwadih lfzana wamaenaa. 'iinaa 'anzalnah fi laylat alqadr almubarakat kathirat alkhayrati, wahi fi ramdanin. 'iinaa kunaa mundhirin alnaas bima yanfaeuhum wayaduruhum, wdhlk bi'iirsal alrusul wa'iinzal alkatba; litaqum hujat allah ealaa eibadih. fiha yuqda wyufsl min allawh almahfuz 'iilaa alktbt min almalayikat kll 'amr mahkum min alajal wal'arzaq fi tilk alsanati, waghayr dhlk mimaa yakun fiha 'iilaa akhiriha, la ybddal wala yghyar. hdha al'amr alhakim 'amr min eindina, fajmie ma yakun wayuqdiruh allah taealaa wama yuhiuh fabi'amarih wa'iidhanih waeilmiha. 'iinaa kunaa mursilin 'iilaa alnaas alrusul mhmdana wamin qabliha; rahmat min rabik -'ayaha alrasula- bialmursil 'iilayhim. 'iinah hu alsamie yasmae jmye al'aswati, alealim bijamie 'umur khalaqah alzzahirat walbatinata. khaliq alsamawat wal'ard wama baynahuma min al'ashya' kulaha, 'iin kuntum muwqinin bdhlk faelamuu 'ana rabi almakhluqat hu 'iilahuha alhuqa. la 'iilah yastahiqu aleibadat 'iilaa hu wahdah la sharik laha, yuhyi waymaytu, rabukum warabu abayikum al'awalina, faebuduh dun alihatakum alty la tuqadar ealaa durin wala nafae"
  44,5,"'uqsim allah taealaa bialquran alwadih lfzana wamaenaa. 'iinaa 'anzalnah fi laylat alqadr almubarakat kathirat alkhayrati, wahi fi ramdanin. 'iinaa kunaa mundhirin alnaas bima yanfaeuhum wayaduruhum, wdhlk bi'iirsal alrusul wa'iinzal alkatba; litaqum hujat allah ealaa eibadih. fiha yuqda wyufsl min allawh almahfuz 'iilaa alktbt min almalayikat kll 'amr mahkum min alajal wal'arzaq fi tilk alsanati, waghayr dhlk mimaa yakun fiha 'iilaa akhiriha, la ybddal wala yghyar. hdha al'amr alhakim 'amr min eindina, fajmie ma yakun wayuqdiruh allah taealaa wama yuhiuh fabi'amarih wa'iidhanih waeilmiha. 'iinaa kunaa mursilin 'iilaa alnaas alrusul mhmdana wamin qabliha; rahmat min rabik -'ayaha alrasula- bialmursil 'iilayhim. 'iinah hu alsamie yasmae jmye al'aswati, alealim bijamie 'umur khalaqah alzzahirat walbatinata. khaliq alsamawat wal'ard wama baynahuma min al'ashya' kulaha, 'iin kuntum muwqinin bdhlk faelamuu 'ana rabi almakhluqat hu 'iilahuha alhuqa. la 'iilah yastahiqu aleibadat 'iilaa hu wahdah la sharik laha, yuhyi waymaytu, rabukum warabu abayikum al'awalina, faebuduh dun alihatakum alty la tuqadar ealaa durin wala nafae"
  44,6,"'uqsim allah taealaa bialquran alwadih lfzana wamaenaa. 'iinaa 'anzalnah fi laylat alqadr almubarakat kathirat alkhayrati, wahi fi ramdanin. 'iinaa kunaa mundhirin alnaas bima yanfaeuhum wayaduruhum, wdhlk bi'iirsal alrusul wa'iinzal alkatba; litaqum hujat allah ealaa eibadih. fiha yuqda wyufsl min allawh almahfuz 'iilaa alktbt min almalayikat kll 'amr mahkum min alajal wal'arzaq fi tilk alsanati, waghayr dhlk mimaa yakun fiha 'iilaa akhiriha, la ybddal wala yghyar. hdha al'amr alhakim 'amr min eindina, fajmie ma yakun wayuqdiruh allah taealaa wama yuhiuh fabi'amarih wa'iidhanih waeilmiha. 'iinaa kunaa mursilin 'iilaa alnaas alrusul mhmdana wamin qabliha; rahmat min rabik -'ayaha alrasula- bialmursil 'iilayhim. 'iinah hu alsamie yasmae jmye al'aswati, alealim bijamie 'umur khalaqah alzzahirat walbatinata. khaliq alsamawat wal'ard wama baynahuma min al'ashya' kulaha, 'iin kuntum muwqinin bdhlk faelamuu 'ana rabi almakhluqat hu 'iilahuha alhuqa. la 'iilah yastahiqu aleibadat 'iilaa hu wahdah la sharik laha, yuhyi waymaytu, rabukum warabu abayikum al'awalina, faebuduh dun alihatakum alty la tuqadar ealaa durin wala nafae"
  44,7,"'uqsim allah taealaa bialquran alwadih lfzana wamaenaa. 'iinaa 'anzalnah fi laylat alqadr almubarakat kathirat alkhayrati, wahi fi ramdanin. 'iinaa kunaa mundhirin alnaas bima yanfaeuhum wayaduruhum, wdhlk bi'iirsal alrusul wa'iinzal alkatba; litaqum hujat allah ealaa eibadih. fiha yuqda wyufsl min allawh almahfuz 'iilaa alktbt min almalayikat kll 'amr mahkum min alajal wal'arzaq fi tilk alsanati, waghayr dhlk mimaa yakun fiha 'iilaa akhiriha, la ybddal wala yghyar. hdha al'amr alhakim 'amr min eindina, fajmie ma yakun wayuqdiruh allah taealaa wama yuhiuh fabi'amarih wa'iidhanih waeilmiha. 'iinaa kunaa mursilin 'iilaa alnaas alrusul mhmdana wamin qabliha; rahmat min rabik -'ayaha alrasula- bialmursil 'iilayhim. 'iinah hu alsamie yasmae jmye al'aswati, alealim bijamie 'umur khalaqah alzzahirat walbatinata. khaliq alsamawat wal'ard wama baynahuma min al'ashya' kulaha, 'iin kuntum muwqinin bdhlk faelamuu 'ana rabi almakhluqat hu 'iilahuha alhuqa. la 'iilah yastahiqu aleibadat 'iilaa hu wahdah la sharik laha, yuhyi waymaytu, rabukum warabu abayikum al'awalina, faebuduh dun alihatakum alty la tuqadar ealaa durin wala nafae"
  44,8,"'uqsim allah taealaa bialquran alwadih lfzana wmena. 'iinaa 'anzalnah fi laylat alqadr almubarakat kathirat alkhyrat, wahi fi rmdan. 'iinaa kunaa mundhirin alnaas bima yanfaeuhum wydrhm, wdhlk bi'iirsal alrusul w'inzal alktb; ltqwm hujat allah ealaa ebadh. fiha yuqda wyufsl min allwh almhfwz 'iilaa alktbt min almalayikat kll 'amr mhkm min alajal walarzaq fi tilk alsnt, waghayr dhlk mimaa yakun fiha 'iilaa akhrha, la ybddal wala yghyar. hdha al'amr alhakim 'amr min endna, fjmye ma yakun wyqdrh allah taealaa wama ywhyh fbamrh w'idhnh welmh. 'iinaa kunaa mursilin 'iilaa alnaas alrusul mhmdana wamin qblh; rahmatan min rabik -ayha alrswl- balmrsl 'ilyhm. 'iinah hu alsamie yasmae jmye alaswat, alealim bjmye 'umur khalaqah alzzahirat walbatn. khaliq alsmwat wal'ard wama baynahuma min al'ashya' klha, 'iin kuntum muwqinin bdhlk faelamuu 'ana rabi almkhlwqat hu 'ilhha alhq. la 'ilh yastahiqu alebadt 'iilaa hu wahdah la sharik lh, yuhyi wymyt, rabukum warabu abayikum alawlyn, faebuduh dun alihatakum alty la tuqadar ealaa durin wala nfe"
  44,9,"bl hwla' almushrikun fi shakin min alhq, fahum yalhun wylebwn, wala yusadiqun bh"
  44,10,"fantzr -ayha alrswl- bhwla' almushrikin yawm tati alsama' bidukhan mubin wadih yemm alnas, wyqal lhm: hdha eadhab mulim mwje, thuma yaqulun saylyn rafaeah wkshfh enhm: rabana akshif eanaa aledhab, fa'iina kshfth eanaa fa'iinaa muwminun bk"
  44,11,"fantzr -ayha alrswl- bhwla' almushrikin yawm tati alsama' bidukhan mubin wadih yemm alnas, wyqal lhm: hdha eadhab mulim mwje, thuma yaqulun saylyn rafaeah wkshfh enhm: rabana akshif eanaa aledhab, fa'iina kshfth eanaa fa'iinaa muwminun bk"
  44,12,"fantzr -ayha alrswl- bhwla' almushrikin yawm tati alsama' bidukhan mubin wadih yemm alnas, wyqal lhm: hdha eadhab mulim mwje, thuma yaqulun saylyn rafaeah wkshfh enhm: rabana akshif eanaa aledhab, fa'iina kshfth eanaa fa'iinaa muwminun bk"
  44,13,"kyf yakun lahum altdhkr walateaz baed nuzul aleadhab bhm, waqad ja'ahum rasul mbyn, wahu muhamad ealayh alsalat walslam, thuma 'aeraduu eanh wqalu: ellamh bashar 'aw alkhnt 'aw alshyatyn, hu majnun walays brswl?"
  44,14,"kyf yakun lahum altdhkr walateaz baed nuzul aleadhab bhm, waqad ja'ahum rasul mbyn, wahu muhamad ealayh alsalat walslam, thuma 'aeraduu eanh wqalu: ellamh bashar 'aw alkhnt 'aw alshyatyn, hu majnun walays brswl?"
  44,15,"snrfe eankum aleadhab qlyla, wstrwn 'anakum taeudun 'iilaa ma kuntum fih min alkufr waldalal waltkdhyb, wa'anana sneaqbkm ealaa dhlk"
  44,16,ywm nueadhib jmye alkufaar aleadhab al'akbar yawm alqiamat wahu yawm antqamna mnhm
  44,17,"wlqd akhtbrna wabtlyna qabl hwla' almushrikin qawm frewn, waja'ahum rasul krym, wahu musaa ealayh alslam, fakadhabuh fhlku, fhkdha nafeal baedayk 'ayuha alrswl, 'iin lam ywmnu"
  44,18,"wqal lahum mwsa: 'an sllimu 'ily eibad allah min bani 'iisrayiyl warslwhm mey; liaebuduu allah wahdah la sharik lh, 'iiniy lakum rasul 'amin ealaa wahyuh wrsalth"
  44,19,"wala ttkbru ealaa allah btkdhyb rslh, 'iiniy atikum bbrhan wadih ealaa sidq rsalty, 'iiniy astjrt biallah rabiy warabukum 'ana tqtlwny rjmana balhjart, wa'iin lam tsdqwny ealaa ma jitukum bih fkhllu sbyly, wkffu ean adhay"
  44,20,"wala ttkbru ealaa allah btkdhyb rslh, 'iiniy atikum bbrhan wadih ealaa sidq rsalty, 'iiniy astjrt biallah rabiy warabukum 'ana tqtlwny rjmana balhjart, wa'iin lam tsdqwny ealaa ma jitukum bih fkhllu sbyly, wkffu ean adhay"
  44,21,"wa'alla ttkbru ealaa allah btkdhyb rslh, 'iiniy atikum bbrhan wadih ealaa sidq rsalty, 'iiniy astjrt biallah rabiy warabukum 'ana tqtlwny rjmana balhjart, wa'iin lam tsdqwny ealaa ma jitukum bih fkhllu sbyly, wkffu ean adhay"
  44,22,fdea musaa rbh- hin kadhibuh fireawn waqawmuh walam yuminuu bh- qayla 'iina hwla' qawm mushrikun biallah kafrwn
  44,23,"f'asr- ya mwsa- bebady- aladhin saddaqwk, waminuu bk, watbewk, dun aladhin kadhabuk mnhm- laylana 'iinakum mutabaeun min fireawn wajunuduh ftnjwn, wyghrq fireawn wjnwdh"
  44,24,"watrk albahr kama hu ealaa halatih alty kan ealayha hin slkth, saknana ghyr mdtrb, 'iina fireawn wajunuduh mughraqun fi albhr"
  44,25,"km tarak fireawn waqawmuh baed muhlikuhum w'ighraq allah 'iiahum min basatin wajanaat nadrt, waeuyun min alma' jaryt, wazurue wamanazil jmylt, weysht kanuu fiha mtnemyn mtrfyn"
  44,26,"km tarak fireawn waqawmuh baed muhlikuhum w'ighraq allah 'iiahum min basatin wajanaat nadrt, waeuyun min alma' jaryt, wazurue wamanazil jmylt, weysht kanuu fiha mtnemyn mtrfyn"
  44,27,"km tarak fireawn waqawmuh baed muhlikuhum w'ighraq allah 'iiahum min basatin wajanaat nadrt, waeuyun min alma' jaryt, wazurue wamanazil jmylt, weysht kanuu fiha mtnemyn mtrfyn"
  44,28,"mthl dhlk aleiqab yeaqb allah man kdhdhab wbddal niemat allah kfrana, wa'awrathna tilk alnaeam min baed fireawn waqawmuh qwmana akharin khlfwhm min bani 'israyyl"
  44,29,"fma bakat alsama' wal'ard hznana ealaa fireawn wqwmh, wama kanuu mwkhkharyn ean aleuqubat alty hllat bhm"